ENAITURUK

Ore embuku e ESRA nesuju embuku oo Ntepen, eutu enchukunoto oo yarunot kuti loo Lyahudi eing'uaa Babilon o enchukunoto enkishui eseremare te Yerusalem. Ore kuna baa nelimuno te kuna rishat: (
1  ) Ilyahudi le dukuya ooiturukutuo eing'uaa Babilon te nkitanapata e Sairos, olaiguanani le Parsia. (
2  ) Enyaakaki aashet Enkaji e Nkai neitisinyi, neitopiuni eseremare te Yerusalem. (
3  ) Ore too larin ootusujutua lelo, neitoki likae turrur orikito Esra alotu Yerusalem. Ore apa Esra naa oltung'ani arriyia too nkitanapat e Nkai laa ninye otaretuo iltung'ana metusuja imbaa e Nkai o enkishon enye e anaake peyie etum aatagolie enkishui e Nkai enjung'ore te Israel.

